text: Hi all! My name is Myra and I'm <http://Supernova.io|Supernova.io>'s CMO, based in Prague, CZ. Previously I worked in the translation technology industry as a Content Marketer and Social Media Manager, and as a Food Writer for Better Homes and Gardens. Ways I could be potentially helpful to you: Offering a vendor/management perspective, framing content marketing in an overall marketing strategy, as well as lead generation and social media strategies. Looking forward to connecting and learning! :hugging_face:

Allison

I'm really happy to be a part of this community. By degree, I am an Art Historian and curator, but my professional career shifted to Digital Marketing.

I'm an SEO Manager and Copywriter, currently working for an agency with clients in the moving, payment, remodeling, and finance industry,  an agency that handles artists and their marketing, as well as a freelancer for clients in many other industries.

I'm looking forward to connecting and exchanging ideas and strategies.
